                            <comment id="168978" author="bogl" created="Mon, 10 Oct 2016 19:02:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;lustre 2.8.0 is missing the &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8241&quot; title=&quot;lustre builds with MOFED 3.3 fail&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-8241&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-8241&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; fix.&lt;br/&gt;
